name: Aditya Raj
about: Aditya Raj is the president of the inquizitive society. He leads the team with a focus on innovation and collaboration, ensuring that all projects are executed efficiently. Aditya is passionate about technology and leadership.

name: Aditya Vikram
about: Aditya Vikram serves as the vice-president, supporting the president and overseeing various initiatives. He has a keen interest in emerging technologies and aims to foster a collaborative environment.

name: Aditya Venkat
about: As the event manager, Aditya Venkat is responsible for organizing and coordinating events. He ensures that each event runs smoothly and engages the community effectively.

name: Sarthak
about: Sai, the tech lead, oversees the technical aspects of the inquizitive society's projects. He is dedicated to ensuring the highest standards of technical excellence and innovation.
